{
  "texts": [
    "We conducted a randomized sampling of 500 music generation prompts from the dataset.",
    "These prompts were then processed by ChatMusician, GPT-3.5, and GPT-4 to assess the success rate at which the outputted ABC notation was correctly formatted and parseable.",
    "To improve the parsing success rates for the GPT series, we prefixed the prompts with the directive \"Please respond in ABC notation.\".",
    "Table 6 presents the comparative success rates across the three systems.",
    "Notably, both ChatMusician and GPT-4 demonstrated success rates exceeding 90%, whereas GPT-3.5 achieved a markedly lower rate of 65.4%."
  ]
}